Charset considerations for Import/Export
• Import, not yet implemented:
  – “Unicode or Windows cp1252 (autodetect)” (_auto)
    ‣ if BOM: UTF-8, UTF-16LE, UTF-16BE, UTF-32LE, UTF-32BE
      and skip BOM
    ‣ if !x[0]:
	if !x[1] UTF-32BE else UTF-16BE
    ‣ if !x[1]:
	if !x[2] UTF-32LE else UTF-16LE
    ‣ else: cp1252
